    "Such attacks apply gradient descent to find the most effective attack prompts (Shin et al., 2020; Geisler et al., 2024; Wichers et al., 2024).",
    "A few gradient-based approaches have also shown promising generalization power when applied to closed-box systems (Zou et al., 2023)."
